Elastic Arts, 3429 W. Diversey Ave. #208 Chicago</p>
<a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/sixty-on-stage-poetry-prose-tickets-1989996337615?aff=oddtdtcreator" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RSVP HERE</a>
<p>Free and all are welcome!</p>
