<p>Come watch episode 1 &amp; 2 of <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt34477971/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>THE LOVERS</em></a> with us and Writer / Director / Star <strong>Daviel Shy</strong>.</p>
<p>Doors open at <strong>6pm</strong> and our screenings begin at <strong>7pm</strong>. Dorothy remains open after the screenings until 11pm.</p>
<p>Dorothy is <strong>21+</strong> and requires physical or mobile ID to enter. Dorothy is also <strong>ADA accessible</strong> with elevator access on Campbell Ave. If you are a guest who requires elevator access, please wait by the black door on Campbell Ave with our logo in the window and call our staff to assist: <strong>773-770-3799</strong></p>
