<p>From erotic and sensual works to expressions of romance and platonic connection—the show celebrates intimacy, desire, and affection in all their forms.</p>
<p>On view February 6, 2026-March 6, 2025 at Chicago Fine Art Salon. Opening reception 5-9pm on February 6, 2026.</p>
